00:45:26.360 --> 00:45:33.320
so wherever you apply that, those skills, it's important to understand that the stakeholders,

00:45:33.320 --> 00:45:38.760
what are the, what are the things we need to consider from real life, you know,

00:45:38.760 --> 00:45:43.560
